<author><name><![CDATA[juniper7]]></name></author>
<updated>2017-10-27T11:04:42-07:00</updated>
<published>2017-10-27T11:04:42-07:00</published>
<id>http://www.classicshell.net/forum/viewtopic.php?t=8054&amp;p=34590#p34590</id>
<link href="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/viewtopic.php?t=8054&amp;p=34590#p34590"/>
<title type="html"><![CDATA[LCARS Tactical [7 style]]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/viewtopic.php?t=8054&amp;p=34590#p34590"><![CDATA[
LCARS Tactical [7style] for CSM version 4.3.0<br /><br /><br /><br />Menu skin was made from elements of Starship Atlantis wallpaper, by TronTrek: <br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://fav.me/d6kbo1l">http://fav.me/d6kbo1l</a><!-- m --><br /><br />It is different from most LCARS wallpapers, due to the extra blue grey colors,<br />which makes it easier on the eyes, but harder to find matching wallpapers.<br /><br />Variation 1 is your typical menu that can be adjusted.<br /><br /><br />Variation 2, 3, 4 use picture emblems for the colored bars on 2nd column.<br />Due to this fact, I have to stress these skin variations will be unusable if any of below requirements do not match:<br /><br /><span style="color:#ff0000;">HAS TO BE 100%, or 150% size</span>. 125% is NOT available <br /><br /><span style="color:#ff0000;">HAS TO BE default settings with 13 menu item entries in right column</span>. Was made for Windows 10, but can work for Win7/8.<br />Just need to go to &quot;Customize Start Menu&quot; tab to set up qty 13 entries to be displayed. 13 is the lucky number. <img src="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/images/smilies/icon_lol.gif" alt=":lol:" title="Laughing" /> <br />It will go out of alignment, and look ugly if other qty.<br /><br />Sorry, one more, and I want to kick myself, for I thought it was default in all operating systems.<br /><span style="color:#ff0000;">This font, Franklin Gothic Medium Cond, HAS TO BE installed</span>. It squeezes up the text a little bit.<br />Without this font, bars go out of alignment, as the text padding is set for it exactly. <br /><br />I initially tried Lcars, Steelfish Rg fonts, but were way too ffuzzzyy to use at such small font sizes. Too bad.<br /><br />The Segoe font option does not work when the multicolor selector bars in 2nd column are showing. <br /><br />Have only tested skin in English. I don't know if other languages change alignment.<br /><br /><br />Note. If this .skin7 is renamed to .skin it will show up in Classic 2 style, and can work.<br />On two of the variations there can be small icons on 2nd column. <br />The &quot;Regular&quot; variation can have large icons. <br /><br />Additional note. I may have buggered up the 2nd column icons text when using Classic 2 style. <br />You might see white folders instead of the regular icons. <br />Click the small icons, and no icons check boxes a couple times to refresh back to normal.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=856">juniper7</a> — Fri Oct 27, 2017 11:04 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
